00:12:30.705 --> 00:12:32.955
They have told us that they're deeply affected

259
00:12:33.095 --> 00:12:35.435
by social comparison, misinformation,

260
00:12:35.575 --> 00:12:38.195
and algorithm driven exposure to harmful content.

261
00:12:39.105 --> 00:12:42.285
