00:26:05.685 --> 00:26:07.565
of put the genie back in the bottle

574
00:26:08.025 --> 00:26:09.845
if you understand my question? Yeah.

575
00:26:10.265 --> 00:26:12.565
Um, so to some extent we are too late.

