00:28:08.805 --> 00:28:10.285
'cause for the vast majority of the time,

626
00:28:10.285 --> 00:28:11.805
kids are using their own devices.

627
00:28:12.145 --> 00:28:14.845
So even if they borrow a friend's phone, that's going

628
00:28:14.845 --> 00:28:18.085
to be a limited amount of their use time compared

629
00:28:18.085 --> 00:28:20.165
to the device that devices that actually belong to them.

630
00:28:20.185 --> 00:28:22.285
And obviously as they get older, this will be less

631
00:28:22.285 --> 00:28:24.245
and less true, but then the wisdom

632
00:28:24.545 --> 00:28:27.325
of regulating in a fairly onerous manner

633
00:28:27.845 --> 00:28:28.925
decreases as they get older.

